comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Walker's (POR) path, and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to roll towards the basket.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is firming up over his left leg and absorbs the contact from Walker (POR) to his upper body.
Banton (POR) cleanly blocks Harris' (ORL) layup attempt.
Ayton (POR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Ayton (POR) moves his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Harris (ORL) legally contests Banton's (POR) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Henderson (POR) brings his hand forward into Suggs' (ORL) front and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Walker (POR) gathers the ball on his right foot and does not take more than two steps after his gather.
Carter Jr. (ORL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from Henderson (POR) during his shot near the rim.
Henderson (POR) steps forward towards Banchero's (ORL) path, and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, which he maintains at the start of his dribble.
Carter Jr. (ORL) roll towards the rim, and marginal contact occurs as Walker (POR) has committed to going under the pick.
Banton (POR) cleanly blocks Carter Jr.'s (ORL) shot attempt near the rim.
Banton (POR) cleanly blocks Carter Jr.'s (ORL) shot attempt before the ball touches the backboard.
Suggs (ORL) moves forward towards Ayton's (POR) side, and the contact as Ayton receives the ball is marginal.
Carter Jr. (ORL) contests Ayton's (POR) shot near the rim, and the contact after the release is marginal.
Suggs (ORL) briefly grasps Henderson's (POR) jersey and immediately releases him as they come together during the drive.
Henderson (POR) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, which he maintains as he pivots in the lane.
Suggs (ORL) initiates contact with Henderson's (POR) arm, and the contact affects Henderson's (POR) shot attempt.
Isaac (ORL) legally contests Ayton's (POR) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
